subject: Boston Marathon
Olympic Games (2012)
Marathon Running
lead_paragraph: Desiree Davila, an also-ran at the 2008 qualifying race, enters Saturday’s U.S. Olympic marathon trials with the fastest qualifying time, 2:22:38.
